Package de.iabg.swing

Interface Summary
Loggable This interface declares basic functionality for an object that can send log strings to registered listeners.
Logger This interface declares basic functionality for an object that can log events.
 

Class Summary
DrawingPanel This implementation of Renderer merges Swing and Java3D into one standard component.
HistoryPanel This Logger creates a Swing component that displays a running command history of all logged actions.
KeyList This ComboBoxModel is backed by an ArrayList since there are several instances where it is convenient to have this combination.
KeyMap This ComboBoxModel is backed by a LinkedHashMap since there are several instances where it is convenient to have this combination.
StatusPanel This Logger creates a Swing component that displays a snapshot view of the last logged item.
